en-IN.name: word cyclopedia
en-IN.description:
Word Cyclopedia Alexa skill is an English dictionary. It explains meaning of English words.

This skill is optimized for screens. So if you are using an Alexa device with screen, you can view meaning of the word displayed beautifully on the screen.

To get meaning of an English word like etymology, say Alexa, ask word cyclopedia to tell me meaning of etymology
